Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:48.11,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不曾忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:55.71,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们曾经一同奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:59.63,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}带着期许
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.36,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.24,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}终将重逢
